    <h1>Web Browser</h1>
    <p><em>A simple web browser application built using Python and PyQt5.</em></p>

    <p><strong>Author:</strong> Bocaletto Luca</p>
    <p><strong>License:</strong> MIT &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="LICENSE">Read LICENSE</a></p>
    <p><strong>Source:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/bocaletto-luca/BrowserWeb">GitHub Repository</a></p>

    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Navigate to websites via URL or search query</li>
      <li>Back and forward navigation controls</li>
      <li>Reload current page</li>
      <li>Home button set to DuckDuckGo</li>
      <li>Advanced privacy settings: disable JavaScript and block third-party resources</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Screenshots</h2>
