    <h2>Installation</h2>
    <pre><code class="language-bash"># Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/bocaletto-luca/BrowserWeb.git
cd BrowserWeb

# Install dependency
pip install PyQt5
</code></pre>

    <h2>Usage</h2>
    <pre><code class="language-bash"># Run the application
python BrowserWeb.py
</code></pre>
    <p>In the address bar enter a URL or search query, then use back/forward, reload and home buttons to navigate.</p>

